# Page 1 Requirements:

1. Create HTML form with Action  
   1. Form must have a minimum of 1 Textbox, with 1 Required field \- 2 pts  
   2. Form must have a Submit Button \- 1 pt  
   3. Form must have an action that redirect to Page 2 on Submission \-  3 pts  
   4. Form must have labels \- 2 pts  
2. CSS:  
   1. Change Background Color of Page \- 1 pt  
   2. CSS Must Style the Submit Button, and ONLY the submit button, with a Different Color, and some margin \- 3 pts  
   3. The Submit button must have a Hover Element (the color changes on hover) \- **CHALLENGE (Not directly covered in Lecture**) \- 6 pts  
   4. You must create a div, and use that to modify the text boxes \- 4 pts  
      1. Make it have a Margin  
      2. Increase the Font-Size of at least the label

# Page 2 Requirements:

1. The page must have a h1, which is aligned to the Center \- 2 pts  
2. There must be an image which has a width of 50% and is Centered \- 4 pts  
3. The page must be a different background color \- 1 pt
